snippet.title: Soulstice - PC Demo Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Soulstice developers' Reply Game Studios’ revealed a demo for the game during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022. The Soulstice demo is available on Steam right now, and the full game is coming to PC, PS5 and Xbox Series X and S on September 20, 2022.
